hole_2.original_tactic:
calc
  ‖z 0 + z 1 + z 2 + z 3‖ ≤ ‖z 0‖ + ‖z 1‖ + ‖z 2‖ + ‖z 3‖ := by
    calc
      ‖z 0 + z 1 + z 2 + z 3‖ ≤ ‖z 0 + z 1 + z 2‖ + ‖z 3‖ := norm_add_le _ _
      _ ≤ ‖z 0 + z 1‖ + ‖z 2‖ + ‖z 3‖ := by gcongr <;> apply norm_add_le
      _ ≤ ‖z 0‖ + ‖z 1‖ + ‖z 2‖ + ‖z 3‖ := by gcongr <;> apply norm_add_le
  _ = 4 := by simp [hzle1] <;> norm_num

hole_4.original_tactic:
calc
  ‖3 + z 0 * z 1 * z 2 * z 3‖ ≤ ‖(3 : ℂ)‖ + ‖z 0 * z 1 * z 2 * z 3‖ := norm_add_le _ _
  _ = 3 + ‖z 0 * z 1 * z 2 * z 3‖ := by simp [Complex.norm_eq_abs]
  _ ≤ 3 + 1 :=
    by
    have h₅ : ‖z 0 * z 1 * z 2 * z 3‖ ≤ 1 := by
      calc
        ‖z 0 * z 1 * z 2 * z 3‖ = ‖z 0‖ * ‖z 1‖ * ‖z 2‖ * ‖z 3‖ := by simp [norm_mul, Complex.abs.map_mul]
        _ = 1 := by simp [hzle1] <;> norm_num
        _ ≤ 1 := by norm_num
    linarith
  _ = 4 := by norm_num
